<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/93/112/s8">section 8 of Pub. L. 93–112</ref> was renumbered section 10 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t29/s707">section 707 of this title</ref>.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Another prior <ref href="/us/pl/93/112/s8">section 8 of Pub. L. 93–112</ref> was classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t29/s707">section 707 of this title</ref> prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/105/220">Pub. L. 105–220</ref>.</p>
</note>
